Package org.jnosql.aphrodite.antlr

This package contains the implementation of JNoSQL query using Antlr4.

Package org.jnosql.aphrodite.antlr Description

This package contains the implementation of JNoSQL query using Antlr4. ANTLR (ANother Tool for Language Recognition) is a powerful parser generator for reading, processing, executing, or translating structured text or binary files.
